{"tid":1223622,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"眾籌買裝，義士不要再埃打受傷","createTime":"2019-06-14T18:00:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T02:16:57.000Z","uid":79325,"like":36,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0f1fe92b1e43cdd353f97a9c0f95d552344569e9","tid":1223622,"uid":79325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T18:00:15.000Z","msg":"5年前我地輸咗，輸人數輸裝備<br />\n5年後，我地人數贏咗，但差佬呢5年嚟不斷不斷咁針對我地訓練<br />\n對住胡椒噴霧，我地只能用又遮抵擋<br />\n對住催淚彈，我地甚至無法招架，只好撤退。今次我地一定要反思一吓我地做錯乜嘢，先可以贏翻香港<br />\n故此琴日開咗個裝備post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1216786/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1216786/page/1</a><br />\n收到迴響係年輕人無乜錢買裝，要用到勞工手套執催淚彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，而防彈裝備就實在係負擔唔到，但實在唔忍心義士們再受傷喇。<br />\n所以想係一個香港眾籌平台(FringeBacker薯片叔叔同民主黨都用過），集資大約10-15萬(5%手續費)，全用在買羊皮軍用手套(防火防熱)同防毒面具，有淨就護膝護肘同盾牌。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LSmf2uE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLSmf2uE.png&h=4efca82e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GUPJrWk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGUPJrWk.png&h=7960bb05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n基於全部都俾前線義士用，所以歡迎有經驗人士留言，俾啲意見"},{"pid":"4bd4ebc4932e1f2c14e9d7dde5047b29fd4d286b","tid":1223622,"uid":62167,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T18:03:35.000Z","msg":"一批訂會唔會充公？"},{"pid":"376b808b645f02d45e10c1ca8535b880dae4c501","tid":1223622,"uid":79325,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T18:05:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"368bc39a88ee5094cc4a4ad0705eb01777a9437b","tid":1223622,"uid":79325,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4bd4ebc4932e1f2c14e9d7dde5047b29fd4d286b","tid":1223622,"uid":62167,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T18:03:35.000Z","msg":"一批訂會唔會充公？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T18:06:05.000Z","m